
  Dusclops    Ghost Type Pokémon

  DUSCLOPS’s body is completely 
  hollow - there is nothing at 
  all inside.  It is said that 
  its body is like a black hole. 
   Dusclops will absorb anything 
  into its body, but nothing will 
  ever come back out. 
	   Evolution Chain
  Duskull ► Dusclops ► Dusknoir

